  title: There Will Be Blood
  genre: Drama 2
  position: 52
  description: "Ruthless silver miner, turned oil prospector, Daniel Plainview, moves
    to oil-rich California. Using his son to project a trustworthy, family-man image,
    Plainview cons local landowners into selling him their valuable properties for
    a pittance. However, local preacher Eli Sunday suspects Plainview\u2019s motives
    and intentions, starting a slow-burning feud that threatens both their lives."
